  "instructions": [
    "Heat vegetable oil in a large saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Add finely chopped onion and sauté until translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "Stir in minced garlic and grated ginger. Cook for another minute.",
    "Fold in mixed peel, cinnamon sticks, and salt. Mix well.",
    "If using sugar or jaggery, mix with the spices. Reduce heat to low and let cook covered for about an hour.",
    "Serve warm as a crumble over rice or as a spread on toast."
